# User Events API

Kafka-based event streaming API for user lifecycle events

HOST: 

## /user.deleted [/user.deleted]

Channel for user deletion events

### Publish user deletion event [POST]

Send a message when a user account is deleted

+ Request (application/json)

## /user.profile.updated [/user.profile.updated]

Channel for user profile update events

### Notified when a user profile is updated [GET]

Consume profile update events

+ Response 200 (application/json)

## /user.signup [/user.signup]

Channel for user signup events

### Notified when a new user signs up [GET]

Consume user signup events from the Kafka topic

+ Response 200 (application/json)

